<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">文档过滤器</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">点击 <span class="link"><a href="documents-search.html" title="搜索文件">搜索</a></span>栏旁边的 <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/go-down.png" class="media media-inline" alt="向下"></span></span> 按钮，在这些类别中限制搜索的范围：</p>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li class="list"><p class="p"><span class="em">来源</span>：本地、Google、SkyDrive 或全部。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p"><span class="em">类型</span>：集合、PDF 文档、演示文稿、电子表格、文本文档或者所有。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">标题，作者或全部。</p></li>
</ul></div></div></div>
<div class="note note-tip" title="提示"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">为了让<span class="gui"> Google </span>或 <span class="gui">SkyDrive</span> 出现在过滤器列表中，需要配置 Google 或 Windows Live 作为一个<span class="link"><a href="accounts-add.html" title="添加账户">在线帐号</a></span>。</p></div></div></div></div>
</div>
